metatab-0.2: The `facilities` file, as downloaded, is severly malformed, with a variable number of columns per row. The extra colums seem to represent a variable number of complain records.  The copy of the file in this package has colums after AK removed.
The two geocoded files were geocoded using sandiego.csv as input, from the Census geocoder lined to https://www.census.gov/geo/maps-data/data/geocoder.html
